					"<span class='gold'>Wear <<if $_plural>>them<<else>>it<</if>> here,</span> if you would be so kind.",
					"If you could <span class='gold'>wear <<if $_plural>>them<<else>>it<</if>> here,</span> that would be wonderful.",
				]>>
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning") and $gwylan.timer.ritual and Time.date.dayDifference(new DateTime($gwylan.timer.ritual)) lte 0>>
					<<set $_conclusions.push("<span class='gold'>Wear <<if $_plural>>them<<else>>it<</if>> here,</span> and maybe I'll rip them right off of you.")>>
				<</if>>
				<<print $_conclusions.pluck()>>
				<<if $_request.details.replacements is "allowed">>
					<<if $_outfit>>They come<<else>>It comes<</if>> in a few different styles, <span class="green">any of them will do</span>."
				<<elseif $_request.details.replacements is "blocked">>
					<<if $_outfit>>They come<<else>>It comes<</if>> in a few different styles, <span class="red">so make sure you get the right one<<if $_plural>>s<</if>>.</span>"
				<<else>>
					<<print either("It should be easy enough.", "No fuss, no muss.", "Go on then, dear.", "I'll owe you.")>>"
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<span class="gold">Gwylan's request has been added to your journal.</span>

		<<case "ingredients">>
			<<if $_request.special is "tutorial">>
				<<set $_shroomAmount to $_request.items.find(shroom => shroom.name === "wolfshroom").need>>
				"Do you know what wolfshrooms are?"
				<br><br>

				<<if $scienceshroomknown is 1 and $scienceproject is "ongoing">>
					You nod. "I was thinking about using them in my current science project at school," you say. "They were popular with warriors in ancient times."
					<br><br>

					"Wonderful! I'm low on stock, and could use a few.
				<<elseif $plants.wolfshroom.amount>>
					You nod. "I've picked them before."
					<br><br>

					"Wonderful! I'm low on stock, and could use a few.
				<<elseif currentSkillValue('science') gte 200>>
					You remember hearing about them from school, and nod. "They were prized by warriors in ancient times," you say.
					<br><br>

					"Wonderful! I'm low on stock, and could use a few.
				<<else>>
					You shake your head.
					<br><br>

					"They're curious little things. Brown stem with a bright red cap. I can tell you more about them later.
				<</if>>
				If you could go find <span class="gold"><<number $_shroomAmount>></span> for me, you'd be making my day much easier."
			<<elseif $_request.special is "plums">>
				"I... have a craving. If you could just be a dear and... and go get me a bunch of plums." <<He>> reaches forward and pinches your cheek. "Please?"
				<br><br>

				<<He>> loweers <<his>> hands, placing them over <<his>> <<bellyDescription "Gwylan">>. "Lots of them. I'm eating for two right now, after all."
			<<else>>
				<<set $_types to []>>
				<<run $_request.items.forEach(item => $_types.pushUnique(item.type))>>
				<<if $_types.length is 1>>
					<<switch $_types[0]>>
						<<case "flower">>
							"My garden needs some genetic diversity, so I've been meaning to pick some wild flowers.
						<<case "fruit">>
							"I need a bunch of fruit for <<print either("fermentation", "seed extraction", "juicing")>>.
						<<case "ingredient">>
							"I need some base ingredients for something I'm mixing together.
						<<case "produce">>
							"I need some produce to use as a binder for... well, don't worry about it."
						<<default>>
							"I need a few <<print $_types[0]>>.
					<</switch>>
				<<elseif $_request.items.every(item => setup.plants[item.name].shop is "supermarket")>>
					"I have a bit of a shopping list here. It's not the most exciting task, but you would be saving me a trip.
				<<else>>
					<<set $_typesPlural to []>>
					<<run $_types.forEach(type => {
						if (type === "produce") {
							$_typesPlural.pushUnique(type)
						} else {
							$_typesPlural.pushUnique(type + "s")
						}
					})>>
					<<set $_typesPlural.push("the like")>>
					<<print either(`"I'm in need of a few ingredients for... well, don't worry about it.`, `"I'm trying something new, so I need a few ingredients.`, `"I'm going to try to make something, so I need a few ingredients.`)>>
					<<print formatList($_typesPlural, "and", true).toUpperFirst()>>.
				<</if>>
				<<set $_names to []>>
				<<run $_request.items.forEach(item => {
					if (item.need > 1) {
						$_names.pushUnique("<<number " + item.need + ">> " + setup.plants[item.name].plural);
					} else {
						if (["a","e","i","o","u"].some(letter => item.name.startsWith(letter))) {
							$_names.pushUnique("an " + setup.plants[item.name].name.replace(/_/g," "));
						} else {
							$_names.pushUnique("a " + setup.plants[item.name].name.replace(/_/g," "));
						}
					}
				})>>
				<span class="gold">I need <<print formatList($_names, "and", true)>>.</span> If you could gather those for me, I would be very thankful."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<span class="gold">Gwylan's request has been added to your journal.</span>

		<<case "sample">>
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("sample")>>
				<<if $gwylan.request.hold is "corruption">>
					"I'll need some fresh <span class="pink">fluid samples</span> to make new measuring charms."
				<<elseif $gwylan.timer.sample gt Time.date.timeStamp>>
					"I'd like to refresh the measuring charms before they burn out. I need another round of <span class="pink">fluid samples</span>."
				<<else>>
					"I need to replace the measuring charms. You know how this goes. I need some fresh <span class="pink">fluid samples</span>."
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				<<if $gwylan.request.hold is "corruption">>
					"In order to measure the taint, I'll need some <span class="pink">fluid samples</span>."
				<<else>>
					"I need to measure the poison in the world. How fast it's growing, and how deep it runs. For this, I need some... samples."
					<<He>> clears <<his>> throat. <span class="pink">"Fluid samples."</span>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<He>> vanishes into a dark room. You hear some clanging, and <<he>> shortly returns with some glass vials. "Not from you.<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("player_sample")>> Not this time, at least.<</if>>
			<<set $_sampleSpecies to []>><<set $_sampleLocations to []>>
			<<run $gwylan.request.items.forEach(item => {
				$_sampleSpecies.pushUnique(item.name);
				if (["human", "dog", "cat"].includes(item.name)) $_sampleLocations.pushUnique("town");
				if (["wolf", "fox", "lizard", "boar", "bear", "plant"].includes(item.name)) $_sampleLocations.pushUnique("forest");
				if (["hawk", "fox", "cat"].includes(item.name)) $_sampleLocations.pushUnique("moor");
				if (["dolphin"].includes(item.name)) $_sampleLocations.pushUnique("ocean");
			})>>
			<<if $_sampleSpecies.length is 1>>
				<<set $_thisSpecies to $gwylan.request.items[0]>>
				<<set $_thisColour to hasSexStat("deviancy", 3) ? "pink" : "red">>
				<<if $_thisSpecies.name is "wolf">>
					<<set $_thisColour to $syndromewolves gte 1 ? "green" : "red">>
				<</if>>
				<<switch $_thisSpecies.name>>
					<<case "human">>I need a diverse array of samples from the <span class="purple">people of the town</span>.
					<<case "wolf">>I need to determine the agitation level of the local <span @class="$_thisColour">wolf pack</span>. I'll need some samples from them.
					<<case "plant">>I need a large amount of nectar samples from the <span class="forest-green">dryads of the forest</span>. If they become tainted, things will become very grim.
					<<case "fox">>The <span @class="$_thisColour">foxes</span> of our forest may be clever, but not even they are immune to the poison. I'll need some samples from them, or from the ones out in the moor.
					<<case "cat">>There's an interesting reaction in feline species, so I need samples from <span @class="$_thisColour">large cats</span>. It doesn't matter whether they're from the town or moor.
					<<case "dolphin">>I worry that the poison has begun leaking into the ocean. I need samples from large marine mammals, such as <span @class="$_thisColour">dolphins</span>.
					<<default>>
						I need a diverse array of samples from the <span @class="$_thisColour"><<print $_thisSpecies.name + "s">></span> of the <<print formatList($_sampleLocations, "and", true)>>.
				<</switch>>
				<span class="gold"><<Number $_thisSpecies.need>></span> <<pluralise $_thisSpecies.need "sample">> should be enough."
			<<else>>
				I need some samples from the <<print formatList($_sampleLocations, "and", true)>>. Specifically, I need
				<<for $_s to 0; $_s lt $_sampleSpecies.length; $_s++>>
					<<set $_thisSpecies to $gwylan.request.items.find(species => species.name === $_sampleSpecies[$_s])>>
					<<switch $_thisSpecies.name>>
						<<case "wolf">><<set $_thisSpeciesPlural to "wolves">>
						<<case "fox">><<set $_thisSpeciesPlural to "foxes">>
						<<case "plant">><<set $_thisSpeciesPlural to "the dryads of the forest">>
						<<default>><<set $_thisSpeciesPlural to $_thisSpecies.name + "s">>
					<</switch>>
					<<switch $_thisSpecies.name>>
						<<case "human">><<set $_thisSpeciesColour to "purple">>
						<<case "wolf">><<set $_thisSpeciesColour to $syndromewolves gte 1 ? "green" : hasSexStat("deviancy", 3) ? "pink" : "red">>
						<<case "plant">><<set $_thisSpeciesColour to "forest-green">>
						<<default>><<set $_thisSpeciesColour to hasSexStat("deviancy", 3) ? "pink" : "red">>
					<</switch>>
					<span class="gold"><<number $_thisSpecies.need>></span>
					<<if $_thisSpecies.name is "plant">>
						nectar
					<<else>>
						<<if maleChance() >= 100>>
							semen
						<<else>>
							fluid
						<</if>>
					<</if>>
					<<pluralise $_thisSpecies.need "sample">> from <span @class="$_thisSpeciesColour"><<print $_thisSpeciesPlural>></span><<if $_s is $_sampleSpecies.length - 2>>, and<<elseif $_s is $_sampleSpecies.length - 1>>."<<else>>,<</if>>
				<</for>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<He>> hands you more vials than you need. <<if $_sampleSpecies.length gt 1>>Each one is labelled with the name of a sample source.<</if>>
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("sample")>>
				"I know you can handle this. You're strong.
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance") or _gwylanStatus.includes("dom")>>
					Still, be safe and come back to me in one piece."
				<<else>>
					Still, be safe."
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				"I'm sorry to ask something so dangerous of you. I can't just use the fluids of those I lure here, as those are always oversaturated.
				The reading wouldn't be accurate. I wouldn't be asking if it wasn't important." <<He>> gives you an encouraging smile. "Be safe, please."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<if $gwylan.request.items.some(item => item.name === "plant")>>
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("plantperson_tip")>>
					<<He>> quickly turns back to you once more. "Oh, remember. You can harvest nectar from the <span class="green">vines</span> of the dryads too. You'll get a lot more that way."
				<<else>>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("plantperson_tip")>>
					<<He>> quickly turns back to you once more. "Oh, one more thing. You can harvest nectar from the <span class="green">vines</span> of the dryads too. You'll get a lot more that way."
				<</if>>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>

			<span class="gold">Gwylan's request has been added to your journal.</span>

		<<case "samplePlayer">>
			/* ToDo: Gwylan */

		<<case "preen">>
			<<if $harpy gte 6>>
				"I'd like to preen your wings.
				<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("preen")>>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("preen")>>
					They're very pretty, and I could use some of the feathers."
				<<else>>
					I need to restock on feathers."
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				<<set $_featherCount to $gwylan.request.items.find(feather => feather.name === "feathers").need>>
				"I need some of the hawk's feathers. They're a very valuable ingredient. <span class="gold"><<Number $_featherCount>></span> should be enough."
				<br><br>

				<span class="gold">Gwylan's request has been added to your journal.</span>
			<</if>>

		<<case "cream">>
			"You've been very helpful to me lately. I think you deserve a treat.
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("cream_lick")>>
				<<if $cat gte 6>>
					<span class="lewd">I'd like to see you put that rough tongue to work again, cat<<girl>>,</span>" <<he>> says with a flushed smile. "Last time was so much fun! I've got more cream to use, too."
				<<else>>
					<span class="lewd">I'd like to see you put that tongue to work again,</span>" <<he>> says with a flushed smile. "Last time was so much fun! I've got more cream to use, too."
				<</if>>
			<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("nectar_lick")>>
				<<if $cat gte 6>>
					<span class="lewd">I'd like to see you put that rough tongue to work again, cat<<girl>>,</span>" <<he>> says with a flushed smile. "Last time was so much fun! I can't spare any nectar this time, but I've got some cream."
				<<else>>
					<span class="lewd">I'd like to see you put that tongue to work again,</span>" <<he>> says with a flushed smile. "Last time was so much fun! I can't spare any nectar this time, but I've got some cream."
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				<<if $cat gte 6>>
					I... <span class="lewd">would like to see what that cat tongue of yours can do</span>," <<he>> says with a flushed smile. "I've got some cream for you."
				<<else>>
					I have a fun idea," <<he>> says with a flushed smile. "I've got some cream from the cafe, and... no, it should be a surprise."
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<His>> eyes remain locked on you. "Just let me know when you're ready. It may become... messy."

		<<case "robin">>
			/* ToDo: Gwylan */

		<<default>>
			Gwylan opens <<his>> mouth to speak. <<He>> opens <<his>> mouth, and holds it. <<He>> then sneezes.
			<br><br>

			"Sorry, what were we talking about?"
			<br><br>

			<span class="red">This is a bug. Please report this.</span>
	<</switch>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanRequestEnd">>
	<<set $_skip to _args[0] is "skip" ? true : false>>
	<<set $_silent to _args[0] is "silent" ? true : false>>
	<<if !$_skip and $gwylan.request.event>>
		<<set $gwylan.requestDone to true>>
		<<set $gwylan.requestCount++>>
		<<set $daily.gwylan.request to true>>
		<<if !$_silent>>
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("request_intro")>>
				<<set $_requestBr to true>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("request_intro")>>
				<<He>> places <<his>> hand under <<his>> chin in thought as <<he>> looks you over.
				<<if $gwylan.request.hold>>
					"I know you already had something you wanted help with, but there's more I can do.
				<<else>>
					"There is something particular I may be able to do for you.
				<</if>>
				<span class="blue">If you ever have troubles with sleep, I know a technique that can help.</span> On a related note,
				<span class="blue">if you ever find yourself entranced by someone else's words, come talk to me.</span> I know ways of <span class="pink">overwriting and erasing</span> such hypnotic impulses."
			<<elseif $gwylan.request.hold>>
				<<set $_requestBr to true>>
				<<He>> puts <<his>> elbows on the counter.
				<<switch $gwylan.request.hold>>
					<<case "peace">>"You had asked me about bringing peace to your inner self."
					<<case "silence">>"We can silence that pest in your ear, now."
					<<case "slumber">>"You said you were having sleep troubles."
					<<case "insight">>"You said you were seeing things?"
					<<case "chastity">>"You wanted help removing a restrictive device, right?"
					<<case "familiar">>
						<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
							"You said you wanted me to release your collar?"
						<<else>>
							"You said you wanted me to release your collar, right? It looks like you don't need help with that anymore."
						<</if>>
					<<case "petBed">>"I'll drag your bed back out right away, if you'd like."
					<<default>>"You already had something in mind, right?"
				<</switch>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion>>
			<<if $_requestBr>>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>
			<<switch $hypnosis_traits.devotion>>
				<<case 1>>
					<<hypnosisText "<span class='lblue'>Completing Gwylan's request fills you with a strange sense of satisfaction.</span><<stress -3>><<trauma -3>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>>">>
				<<case 2>>
					<<hypnosisText "<span class='teal'>Completing Gwylan's request fills you with satisfaction.</span><<stress -6>><<trauma -6>><<lstress>><<ltrauma>>">>
				<<case 3>>
					<<hypnosisText "<span class='green'>Gwylan smiles at you proudly. It makes you feel warm and fulfilled.</span><<stress -6>><<trauma -10>><<hallucinogen 50>><<lstress>><<lltrauma>><<ghallucinogens>>">>
				<<case 4>>
					<<hypnosisText "<span class='purple'>Gwylan's warm smile makes your heart skip a beat. You've made <<him>> happy, which makes you happy in turn.</span><<trauma -12>><<arousal 1000>><<hallucinogen 80>><<lltrauma>><<garousal>><<ghallucinogens>>">>
				<<default>>
					<<hypnosisText "<span class='pink'>Gwylan's proud smile nearly brings you to your knees. You're awash with primal fulfillment.</span><<trauma -16>><<arousal 3000>><<drugs 80>><<lltrauma>><<gggarousal>><<gdrugged>>">>
			<</switch>>
		<</if>>
		/* Save as recently completed task for use later */
		<<set $gwylan.timer[$gwylan.request.event] to new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(14).timeStamp>>
		<<set $gwylan.timer.requestLast to Time.date.timeStamp>>
	<</if>>
	<<set $gwylan.requestLast to $gwylan.request>>
	<<set $gwylan.request to {}>>
	<<if $gwylan.requestSeed isnot undefined>>
		<<set $_seedIncrement to 0.001>>
		<<set $gwylan.requestSeed to (($gwylan.requestSeed - 0.25 + $_seedIncrement) % (0.99 - 0.25)) + 0.25>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanChastityRequest">>
	<<set $_consensual to _args[0] or 0>>
	<<if $_consensual is 0 or _gwylanStatus.includes("lust")>>
		<<if !$gwylan.request.event>>
			<<He>> thinks for a moment, then smiles.
			<br><br>

			"<<pcPetname "Gwylan">>, either get that chastity device removed, or come see me later and I'll break it off of you."
			<<run gwylanRequest("chastity")>>
			<<set V.gwylan.request.command to true>>
			<<set V.gwylan.request.timer = new DateTime(Time.date).addDays(1).timeStamp>>
			<<if $combat is 1>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 10>><</if>> /* Partially negates lust loss from ejaculation */
			<br><br>

			<span class="gold">Gwylan's request has been added to your journal.</span>
		<<elseif $gwylan.request.event is "chastity" and $gwylan.request.command>>
			<<He>> looks down at you with a hint of annoyance. "I told you to remove that."
		<<else>>
			<<He>> looks down, annoyed.
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>

<<widget "gwylanJournalItems">>
	<<set $_itemsToList to $gwylan.request.items?.filter(item => !item.skip && !item.alt)>>
	<<if $_itemsToList?.length>>
		<<for $_requestIndex to 0; $_requestIndex lt $_itemsToList.length; $_requestIndex++>>
			<<set $_thisItem to $_itemsToList[$_requestIndex]>>
			<<switch $_thisItem.category>>
				<<case "clothing">>
					<<set $_thisItemSetup to clone(setup.clothes[$_thisItem.slot].find(it => it.name === $_thisItem.name))>>
					<<set $_thisItemSetup.colour to $_thisItem.colour_requirement isnot "any" ? $_thisItem.colour_requirement : $_thisItemSetup.colour_options.random()>>
					<<set $_thisItemSetup.accessory_colour to $_thisItem.acc_colour_requirement isnot "any" ? $_thisItem.acc_colour_requirement : $_thisItemSetup.accessory_colour_options.random()>>
					<<if gwylanRequestClothingSlotCheck($_thisItem.slot)>>
						<span class='fa-icon fa-selected'></span>
					<<else>>
						<span class='fa-icon fa-unselected'></span>
					<</if>>
					<<clothingicon $_thisItemSetup $_thisItem.slot>>
					<<print $_thisItemSetup.name_cap>>
					<<if $_thisItem.slot is "neck" and $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1>>
						<span class="forest-green">or your familiar collar</span>
					<<elseif $_thisItemSetup.shopGroup and $gwylan.request.details?.replacements is "allowed">>
						<span class="green">or a variant</span>
					<<elseif $_thisItemSetup.shopGroup and $gwylan.request.details?.replacements is "blocked">>
						<span class="red">(specific variant)</span>
					<</if>>
					<<if $_thisItem.colour_requirement is "any" and $_thisItem.acc_colour_requirement is "any" and ($_thisItemSetup.colour_options.length or $_thisItemSetup.accessory_colour_options.length)>>
						(any colours)
					<<elseif $_thisItemSetup.colour_options.length or $_thisItemSetup.accessory_colour_options.length>>
						(<<if $_thisItemSetup.colour_options.length>><span @class='$_thisItem.colour_requirement'><<print $_thisItem.colour_requirement>> primary</span><</if>><<if $_thisItemSetup.colour_options.length and $_thisItemSetup.accessory_colour_options.length>> and <</if>><<if $_thisItemSetup.accessory_colour_options.length>><span @class='$_thisItem.acc_colour_requirement'><<print $_thisItem.acc_colour_requirement>> accessory</span><</if>>)
					<</if>>
					<<if ["upper", "lower", "under_upper", "under_lower"].includes($_thisItem.slot)>>
						<<switch $_thisItem.integrity_word>>
							<<case "any">>(any condition)
							<<case "full">><span class="green">(full)</span>
							<<case "frayed">><span class="teal">(frayed)</span>
							<<case "torn">><span class="purple">(torn)</span>
							<<case "tattered">><span class="red">(tattered)</span>
						<</switch>>
					<</if>>
				<<case "tending">>
					<<set $_itemAmount to $plants[$_thisItem.name].amount>>
					<<if $gwylan.request.special is "tutorial">>
						<<set $_itemAmount += $gwylanTutorialShrooms>>
					<</if>>
					<<if $_itemAmount gte $_thisItem.need>>
						<span class='fa-icon fa-selected'></span>
					<<else>>
						<span class='fa-icon fa-unselected'></span>
					<</if>>
					<<set $_thisItemIcon to setup.plants[$_thisItem.name].icon.replace(/\.[^/.]+$/, "")>>
					<<tendingicon $_thisItemIcon>>
					<<number $_thisItem.need>>
					<<if $_thisItem.need gt 1>>
						<<print setup.plants[$_thisItem.name].plural>>
					<<else>>
						<<print setup.plants[$_thisItem.name].name.replace(/_/g," ")>>
					<</if>>
					<<if $_itemAmount gte $_thisItem.need>>
						<span class='green'>($_itemAmount / $_thisItem.need)</span>
					<<elseif $_itemAmount is 0>>
						<span class='red'>($_itemAmount / $_thisItem.need)</span>
					<<else>>
						<span class='blue'>($_itemAmount / $_thisItem.need)</span>
					<</if>>
				<<case "sample">>
					<<if $_thisItem.have gte $_thisItem.need>>
						<span class='fa-icon fa-selected'></span>
					<<else>>
						<span class='fa-icon fa-unselected'></span>
					<</if>>
					<span class="gold"><<Number $_thisItem.need>></span>
					<<if $_thisItem.name is "plant">>
						nectar
					<<elseif maleChance() gte 100>>
						semen
					<<else>>
						lewd fluid
					<</if>>
					<<pluralise $_thisItem.need "sample">> from
					<<set $_sampleColour to $_thisItem.name is "wolf" and $syndromewolves gte 1 ? "green" : hasSexStat("deviancy", 3) ? "pink" : "red">>
					<<switch $_thisItem.name>>
						<<case "human">><span class="purple">humans</span>.
						<<case "plant">><span class="forest-green">plantpeople,</span> or their tentacles.
						<<case "wolf">><span @class="$_sampleColour">wolves</span>.
						<<case "fox">><span @class="$_sampleColour">foxes</span>.
						<<default>><span @class="$_sampleColour"><<print $_thisItem.name + "s">></span>.
					<</switch>>
					<<if $_thisItem.have lt $_thisItem.need>>
						You have <span class="blue"><<number $_thisItem.have>></span>.
					<</if>>
				<<default>>
			<</switch>>
			<br>
		<</for>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>
